Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections

Class BaseCollection<Value>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.BaseCollection<Value>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Countable, Addable<Value>, Emptiness, Joinable<Value>, Sequence<Value>, Sized, SpaceLimited, Zeroable, AsString, StringFormattable, Iterable<Value>, Collection<Value>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseList, BaseSet
public abstract class BaseCollection<Value> extends Object implements Addable<Value>, Collection<Value>, Countable, Joinable<Value>, Sequence<Value>, Sized, StringFormattable
Base class for all KivaKit collections.

A set with a maximum size. Adds useful methods to the usual Set operations, as well as implementing:

  • Addable
  • Collection
  • Countable
  • Joinable
  • Sequence
  • Sized
  • Joinable
  • StringFormattable
